title: Schedule A Tour-Newly Renovated Apartment Homes And Luxury Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
